Tumbleweeds;;65;;82;;PG-13;;Whenever trouble strikes in one of her relationships, single mother Mary Jo Walker (Janet McTeer) and her daughter, Ava (Kimberly J. Brown), pack up and move to another city, a routine Ava is tiring of. This time, they are helped on their move to San Diego by trucker Jack Ranson (Gavin O'Connor). While Ava settles in, getting a leading part in the school play, Jack starts dating Mary Jo but soon reveals himself to be controlling and aggressive. Mary Jo prepares to flee again, angering Ava.;;Drama;;Gavin O'Connor;;1999;;Janet McTeer,Kimberly J. Brown,Gavin O'Connor,Jay O. Sanders,Lois Smith,Laurel Holloman,Michael J. Pollard,Noah Emmerich,Ashley Buccille,Cody McMains;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1093901-tumbleweeds